  "detailed_description": "<h1>PLAY NOW!</h1><p></p><br><h1>WISHLIST NOW!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Explore the forgotten levels of Banban’s Kindergarten. Survive the new terrors that reside below. Uncover the truth behind the place, and find the whereabouts of your missing child…</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/39471c55bce34edec4e743d09dcff075.poster.avif?t=1750914490\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/39471c55bce34edec4e743d09dcff075.webm?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/39471c55bce34edec4e743d09dcff075.mp4?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive the never-entered levels of Banban’s Kindergarten:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the events of Garten of Banban 4, you are forced to run away and delve even deeper into the mysterious establishment that is Banban’s kindergarten. You are heading down to where no human dares to be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/eef9b3d8d33c3a083dc483c89654df0d.poster.avif?t=1750914490\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/eef9b3d8d33c3a083dc483c89654df0d.webm?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/eef9b3d8d33c3a083dc483c89654df0d.mp4?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/5426938602b9e093ffd132cf434a459c.poster.avif?t=1750914490\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/5426938602b9e093ffd132cf434a459c.webm?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/5426938602b9e093ffd132cf434a459c.mp4?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No more friends to make…</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have run out of friends to make. From now on, you only meet new enemies who will make sure you never feel alone! In Banban’s Kindergarten, there are enemies to be made in every corner!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/c84f894fe8986c1c06608ecdd77462e5.poster.avif?t=1750914490\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/c84f894fe8986c1c06608ecdd77462e5.webm?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/c84f894fe8986c1c06608ecdd77462e5.mp4?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/feefc2c87cc397e429c49855b3be077f.poster.avif?t=1750914490\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/feefc2c87cc397e429c49855b3be077f.webm?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499800/extras/feefc2c87cc397e429c49855b3be077f.mp4?t=1750914490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
